
Given that I'm a registerd rescurer for GHRN(Good Hands Rescue Network) and a request comes in that I am avaiable and able to service on my way to another destination.
When I choose to accept the request.
Then the system confirms that I've chosen to accept the request and sends the driver an alrt that I am on my way.


Given that I'm a registerd rescurer for GHRN(Good Hands Rescue Network) and have accepted a request from a driver
When I click on the drivers profile
Then the system reveals the drivers car make and model, license plate, and assistance needs.
